      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is an exemplary specimen of automotive excellence, maintained to a standard that transcends the typical market offering. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, exhibiting no discernible wear and reflecting a history of meticulous stewardship. For the discerning buyer who demands uncompromising quality and investment-grade preservation, this represents a premier opportunity to acquire a peerless asset.",
